EntityDefinitions.MobileOfflineFilters:
<fetch version="1.0" output-format="xml-platform" mapping="logical" distinct="false">
			<entity name="account">
				<filter type="and">
					<condition attribute="modifiedon" operator="last-x-days" value="10"/>
				</filter>
			</entity>
		</fetch>
